Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.36,0:15:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,非常痛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.44,0:15:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道  你不要說了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.58,0:15:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,掉下來了…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.16,0:15:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我明明很擅長爬樹的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.62,0:15:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼回事…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.51,0:15:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,變得不痛了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.79,0:15:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我會怎麼樣呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.73,0:15:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,不痛的話就一定會沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.06,0:15:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.61,0:15:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,身體無法動呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.76,0:15:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,不動也無所謂  我會帶你去的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.21,0:16:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,不過  無法動的話就沒法玩了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.55,0:16:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,祐一…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.69,0:16:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,還會再與我一起玩嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.93,0:16:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,啊  當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.84,0:16:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我還有東西要給亞由呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.73,0:16:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,好高興…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.45,0:16:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,一言為定…
